Odaily Planet Daily News: Sunil, the representative of FTX creditors, posted on the X platform that FTX Estate sold 41 million locked SOL in three auctions, and 12 million SOL will be unlocked on March/April 25.
The buyers are:
1. Galaxy: the largest buyer, bought 25.5 million Solana at $64 (current price is $192);
2. Pantera and other buyers bought at $95;
3. Multiple buyers including Figure, at a price of $102.
